      "name": "Edge Imp Sabres",
      "effect": "If this card is in your GY: You can place 1 card from your hand on the top of the Deck; Special Summon this card in Defense Position. You can only use this effect of \"Edge Imp Sabres\" once per turn."
    },
    "fr": {
